smuggling enough opium into the country to backstop

377
00:28:44,460 --> 00:28:48,460
利用走私大量的鴉片到這個國家 來支持並發動了一場血腥的軍事政變
a very bloody military coup that we would eventually stage a decade later.

378
00:28:48,500 --> 00:28:51,050
所有這些通常都是最高機密
This is all mostly declassified, mostly.

379
00:28:51,420 --> 00:28:54,340
不管怎樣
At any rate, I find myself

380
00:28:54,380 --> 00:28:56,960
我在仰光郊外的叢林裡
in the jungle outside Rangoon,

381
00:28:57,000 --> 00:29:01,920
