So there I am,

384
00:29:06,930 --> 00:29:11,130
是一群骯髒的 瘋狂的
on the verge of being overrun by a bunch of machete-wielding rebels

385
00:29:11,170 --> 00:29:13,920
揮舞著彎刀的叛亂分子
who have terrible attitudes and even worse hygiene

386
00:29:14,210 --> 00:29:17,500
而我只能在36個小時不眠不休的情況下
and all I have is a Remington Buckmaster with a shot-out scope

387
00:29:17,550 --> 00:29:20,800
用一杆帶狙擊鏡的刺刀步槍去苛求勝利
and 36 sleepless hours in which to squeeze out a win.

388
00:29:23,590 --> 00:29:24,710
