like a steam whistle.

391
00:29:35,750 --> 00:29:37,090
一頭能讓你嚇得尿褲子的
Wild boar.

392
00:29:38,670 --> 00:29:40,550
大野豬
Make you piss your pants.

393
00:29:42,170 --> 00:29:44,420
光是聲音就足以讓叛軍四散
The sound alone is enough to make the rebels scatter.

394
00:29:44,460 --> 00:29:46,670
沒人敢去觸碰那些鋒利的獠牙
No one wants to fuck with the tusks.

395
00:29:47,210 --> 00:29:51,170
而那頭那個狗娘養的畜生聞到了我的味道 直奔我而來
So now this son-of-a-bitch gets a sniff of me and comes at me straight away.

396
00:29:52,420 --> 00:29:54,750
我寧肯對付十個兇惡的敵人 也不願面對這一隻野獸
Now I'd rather put a bullet in ten men than kill an animal,

397
00:29:54,770 --> 00:29:56,380
但我還沒來得及現身
but before I'm even presented

398
00:29:56,420 --> 00:30:00,960
一條近6米長的緬甸蟒蛇從榕樹上竄下來
with the do-or-die of it all, an 18 foot Burmese Python

399
00:30:01,000 --> 00:30:06,500
把這頭狂暴的野豬像聖誕火腿一樣纏繞起來
comes down from a banyan tree and wraps up this raging hog like a Christmas ham.

400
00:30:08,380 --> 00:30:10,050
我從沒見過這樣的情形
I've never seen anything like it.

401
00:30:10,670 --> 00:30:13,860
接下來的幾個小時 我就驚奇地看著
And for the next few hours, I watch in wonder as this

402
00:30:13,900 --> 00:30:16,700
黑蟒如何吞咽 豬如何被消化
snake slowly suffocates and devours this pig.

403
00:30:18,300 --> 00:30:20,750
周圍一片寂靜 我什麼都能聽見
It was oddly quiet so I could hear everything.

404
00:30:20,800 --> 00:30:25,460
野豬的骨頭啪啪作響 當它的肺崩潰時
The boar's bones snapping, the bellow's-like wheeze as its lungs collapsed

405
00:30:25,500 --> 00:30:28,000
風箱般的喘息聲使它聽起來像蛇在笑
that made it sound like the snake was laughing.

406
00:30:30,670 --> 00:30:36,550
這仍然是我所見過的最令人驚詫的暴力行為
It remains the most awe-inspiring act of violence I have ever seen.

407
00:30:37,500 --> 00:30:39,630
但我印象最深刻的
But what struck me most

408
00:30:39,960 --> 00:30:45,050
是即使巨蟒張開了它的嘴 要吃掉它的獵物
even as the python extended its jaws a full two feet to devour its prey,

409
00:30:47,050 --> 00:30:51,050
她的眼睛裡仍透著鎮靜和冷酷的算計
was the calm and calculation in its eyes.

410
00:30:54,090 --> 00:30:58,340
直到後來當它移動身體中部
And wasn't until later, when it finally moved its mid-section

411
00:30:58,380 --> 00:31:00,380
透過野豬的拱形輪廓
now distended with the outline of that boar

412
00:31:00,960 --> 00:31:02,550
我看到了一窩蛋
that I saw a dozen eggs.

413
00:31:03,170 --> 00:31:04,380
蟒蛇蛋
Python eggs.

414
00:31:06,090 --> 00:31:08,670
