01:28:26,130 --> 01:28:28,800
他喜歡狗 尤其是哈巴狗
He loves dogs, especially pugs

1111
01:28:29,710 --> 01:28:31,800
他覺得你們應該養一隻
and he thinks you two should rescue one.

1112
01:28:33,550 --> 01:28:38,500
大約一年前他用水彩畫了
梵古的星空之夜給你 祝你生日快樂
He did a watercolor version of Van Gogh's 'Starry Night' about a year ago

1113
01:28:38,550 --> 01:28:41,170
因為他知道 那是你最喜歡的畫
for your birthday because he knew it was your favourite painting.

1114
01:28:43,340 --> 01:28:47,090
他覺得媽媽工作太多 微笑太少
He thinks mom works too much and doesn't smile enough

1115
01:28:50,420 --> 01:28:52,750
但這個男孩真的非常愛你
But that boy loves you so much.

1116
01:28:58,550 --> 01:29:00,420
我怎樣才能終止這玩意兒 傑瑪
How do I stop this, Jemma?

1117
01:29:05,170 --> 01:29:09,050
這不是終止 羅伊 是重置
It's not about stopping, Roy. It's about restarting.

1118
01:29:11,340 --> 01:29:16,420
我用你的DNA作了主軸內缺失的部分
I made your dimensions, your DNA specific to the missing mass within the spindle.

1119
01:29:16,670 --> 01:29:17,850
-這是什麼意思
What does that mean?

1120
01:29:17,880 --> 01:29:22,550
-你必須進入主軸的核心
It means you have to enter the Spindle's core, then theoretically

1121
01:29:23,210 --> 01:29:27,550
接著 理論上 時空將會連續重置並恢復到正常
the time-space continuum should reset and resume.

1122
01:29:28,170 --> 01:29:31,550
-理論上？ -我不知道
- Theoretically? - I don't know.

1123
01:29:32,380 --> 01:29:34,000
說實話我不知道羅伊
I honestly don't, Roy.

1124
01:29:34,050 --> 01:29:37,920
整件事都是匆忙中決定的 我只是想阻止文托
This whole thing's so cobbled together. I was just trying to stop Ventor.

1125
01:29:38,210 --> 01:29:41,000
我甚至都不知道 它是否會有效 直到你出現
I didn't even know it worked until you showed up.

1126
01:29:42,170 --> 01:29:45,670
我只記得 我昨晚剛剛見過你
You have to remember, I just saw you yesterday.

1127
01:29:46,630 --> 01:29:49,000
而我已經很久都沒見過你了
And I haven't seen you in forever.

1128
01:29:51,340 --> 01:29:54,670
我不知道還能做什麼還能去哪裡
I didn't know what else to do, where else to turn.

1129
01:29:57,710 --> 01:30:01,550
我知道你是誰
I just knew the man you were.

1130
01:30:03,420 --> 01:30:05,380
我知道你是什麼樣的人
I know the man you are.

1131
01:30:07,090 --> 01:30:10,250
但我不知道如果你去了機器裡面你會怎麼樣
But I don't know what will happen to you if you go in there.

1132
01:30:13,800 --> 01:30:15,960
但我知道如果我不去的話會發生什麼
But I know what happens if I don't.

1133
01:30:21,750 --> 01:30:24,590
你見過了世界的終結
You saw it? The end of the world?

1134
01:30:24,630 --> 01:30:29,800
-對 -是什麼樣子
- Yeah. - What was it like?

1135
01:30:31,750 --> 01:30:36,630
它比你能想像到最不可思議的還要糟糕一百萬倍
It was everything you imagine it to be, only a million times worse.

1136
01:30:41,590 --> 01:30:45,500
如果我走進這個機器 那什麼都會正常嗎
Will it go forward? If I walk through this thing

1137
01:30:45,550 --> 01:30:48,300
它會重置嗎 你和喬是不是就安全了
Is it gonna reset? Are you and Joe gonna be safe?

1138
01:30:50,050 --> 01:30:53,000
如果你讓你的部分品質回歸到機器的核心 它就會重置
If you return your mass to the core, it should.

1139
01:30:53,550 --> 01:30:55,300
但有可能會失敗
You may not make it.

1140
01:30:55,920 --> 01:30:57,380
你可能會不復存在
You may cease to be.

1141
01:30:58,420 --> 01:30:59,590
那
Well then...

1142
01:31:01,340 --> 01:31:03,420
親我一下 說你愛我
Give me a kiss and tell me you love me.

1143
01:31:14,300 --> 01:31:16,000
我愛你
I love you.

1144
01:31:29,550 --> 01:31:34,550
-等著我 好嗎 -我會的
- Wait for me, huh? - I will.

1145
01:31:38,630 --> 01:31:41,420
媽了個巴子 老子要上了
What the hell. Here we go.


